message.body: eh, just another day! i spent most of it sleeping. had dinner with my parents and saw gatsby after. how's the house? how's good ol knuckles?
That sounds perfect, actually. What did you get for dinner? House is awesome. I got 8/9 rooms clean. I've had four bowls of shisha in the past two days, so I'm
probably going to die. And Nakul has been in DC since Friday, so I don't really know.
i really hope you don't die. and oh yeah, i forgot he was traveling with aditya and ashley, right? we went to panera... not classy. also totally proud of you for the cleaning thing!
